Text: Eta, you awake?
...Yeah...I am.
Did you complete that thing I asked for?
That thing? Yeah. That silver box...over there.
Make sure to...write up a report...on how it works...
Got it. Should I categorize each type I deep-fry?
...That'd be ideal.
Alright. Thanks for lending it to me.
Those footsteps...
...My guess is it's Gamma.
Eeeetaaaa!!!
Quiet down... You're shouting...

Of course I am! How the heck did you rack up all
these expenses last week?!
Expenses...?

I always knew you had a spending problem...but I
never expected it to be this extreme!

Didn't I make it clear last time with the golems that
you can't touch the Garden's operating funds?!

...Wait, you mean she used the Garden's reserves to
pay for her research?
That's exactly what I mean!
Research...and splurging...are inseparable!
Don't sound so smug about it!

Just when we're pushing to increase our war chest to
buy up shares in the capital and launch our business...

If we use up our reserves at this rate, we won't be
able to purchase the all-important shares by the
deadline! What a complete disaster!

Sounds like a problem between the two of you. I'd
best not get involved.

Besides, I'm one of the people benefiting from Eta's
research, so...

What?! Hold on...are you talking about this metal box
right here?

It's a fryer designed for outdoor use. It uses magic
to heat oil safely.

A fryer... Is it part of the food research for our
troops? Doesn't sound like anything related to
your intelligence activities.
Not related to either, and there's no grand purpose.

I'm just taking it with me to the ocean near the
capital for a little experiment.

I want to try out different things I learned from
Master Shadow.
From Master Shadow?
Mind me asking why the ocean near the capital, Zeta?
Huh? Um...for fishing.
Fishing?!
Eta?
That's it... The answer is..."fishing"!
What's the matter? You look unusually awake.
I've solved...Master's riddle!

"What do Midgar tuna and experimental materials have
in common? Ask your heart. The answer...will illuminate
your path forward!"
Aaah!!!

The timing of Zeta's experiment to test Shadow
Wisdom...

Plus, the Midgar tuna...the significance of Zeta's
visit to the capital...the thriving fishing industry
in the capital..."The answer shall illuminate...your
path forward!"

Perhaps Master Shadow is providing a hint for our new
business meant to coincide with us buying up shares!

Both tuna...and the experimental materials...are
related to fishing!
An odd...coincidence! I'm...a little...curious!

Just to be clear, are you two planning on tagging
along?
Of course!
It's a hassle, but...I guess!
Jeez...
...Fine. Just try not to get in my way.

I leave in an hour. I won't wait up, so you'd better
be ready by then.
Understood!
Fine...
Things have taken a strange turn...
Oh well.
